{"tid":826340,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺好多餐廳都消費緊香港個名？","createTime":"2018-09-18T07:43:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-19T01:42:53.000Z","uid":71237,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a067fa6e3526dad622d47b686e3f23f539570bf7","tid":826340,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T07:43:03.000Z","msg":"睇個名已經feel到一班老屎忽無哂創意，諗唔到新餐廳叫咩名，淨係識得消費香港個名。<br />\n老屎忽以為賣香港情懷，求其提供啲低質素茶餐廳食物就一定掂。<br />\n<br />\n香港地 Hong Kong Day<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.openrice.com/zh/hongkong/restaurants?chainId=10004025\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.openrice.com%2Fzh%2Fhongkong%2Frestaurants%3FchainId%3D10004025&d=wThkQtlCs4CCG4tZtdijlcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=f525f754\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.openrice.com/zh/hongkong/restaurants?chainId=10004025</a><br />\n<br />\n美心香港地 Maxim's Hong Kong Day<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.openrice.com/zh/hongkong/restaurants?chainId=10001100\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.openrice.com%2Fzh%2Fhongkong%2Frestaurants%3FchainId%3D10001100&d=wThkQtlCs4CCG4tZtdijlcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=262da280\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.openrice.com/zh/hongkong/restaurants?chainId=10001100</a><br />\n<br />\n香港18餐廳<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.openrice.com/zh/hongkong/restaurants?chainId=10003386\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.openrice.com%2Fzh%2Fhongkong%2Frestaurants%3FchainId%3D10003386&d=wThkQtlCs4CCG4tZtdijlcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=d5248f1b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.openrice.com/zh/hongkong/restaurants?chainId=10003386</a><br />\n<br />\n香港達人 Hong Kong Diner<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.openrice.com/zh/hongkong/restaurants?chainId=10002529\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.openrice.com%2Fzh%2Fhongkong%2Frestaurants%3FchainId%3D10002529&d=wThkQtlCs4CCG4tZtdijlcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=ffcd13f7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.openrice.com/zh/hongkong/restaurants?chainId=1